OL,3,CAlmost two-thirds of Brits would back
OL,4,Csmoke and vape-free pub gardens, poll
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FAlmost two-thirds of people in Britain
OL,8,Fwould back a ban on smoking in pub
OL,9,Fgardens, according to a new YouGov
OL,10,Fsurvey.
OL,12,FThe move would be one of a handful of
OL,13,F"common sense" next steps to "support
OL,14,Fa smoke-free generation", according to
OL,15,Fthe charity Action on Smoking and
OL,16,FHealth (Ash).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
