CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778666815
OL,3,CAlmost two-thirds of Brits would back
OL,4,Csmoke and vape-free pub gardens, poll
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe majority of people also backed a
OL,8,Fban on smoking in areas such as
OL,9,Funiversity campuses and bus stops,
OL,10,Fwhile more than nine in 10 said smoke-
OL,11,Ffree laws should be extended to
OL,12,Fchildren's play areas.
OL,14,FLast month, the UK became the first
OL,15,Fcountry in Europe to bring in laws to
OL,16,Fprevent children aged 17 or younger
OL,17,Ffrom ever legally buying cigarettes as
OL,18,Fthe Tobacco and Vapes Bill was given
OL,19,Froyal assent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
