PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778666815
OL,3,CAlmost two-thirds of Brits would back
OL,4,Csmoke and vape-free pub gardens, poll
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FA government consultation seeking
OL,8,Fviews on extending smoke-free laws to
OL,9,Fcertain outdoor spaces, such as
OL,10,Fplaygrounds or outside hospitals, as
OL,11,Fwell as creating vape-free spaces,
OL,12,Falso closed on May 8.
OL,14,FThe poll of 13,259 people, conducted
OL,15,Ffor Ash, found 93% of adults supported
OL,16,Fsmoke-free playgrounds, along with 78%
OL,17,Fwho backed smoke-free bus stops.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
