PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778666815
OL,3,CAlmost two-thirds of Brits would back
OL,4,Csmoke and vape-free pub gardens, poll
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSome 62% said they would support smoke-
OL,8,Ffree laws being extended to outdoor
OL,9,Fhospitality areas, such as pub
OL,10,Fgardens, while 68% supported smoke-
OL,11,Ffree university and college campuses.
OL,13,FHazel Cheeseman, chief executive of
OL,14,FAsh, said: "Smoke-free laws have been
OL,15,Fone of the biggest public health
OL,16,Fsuccess stories in recent decades, but
OL,17,Fmillions of people are still exposed
OL,18,Fto harmful second-hand smoke in
OL,19,Foutdoor settings.
OL,26,@vD@LOU
