OL,3,CAlmost two-thirds of Brits would back
OL,4,Csmoke and vape-free pub gardens, poll
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F'The public is clear that they want
OL,8,Fmore places where they can breathe
OL,9,Fclean air'
OL,11,FGovernment estimates suggest the
OL,12,FTobacco and Vapes Bill could slash the
OL,13,Ftotal number of smokers aged 14 and
OL,14,Fover to 700,000 in 2056 from 5.5
OL,15,Fmillion back in 2023.
OL,17,FThe modelling also estimates that over
OL,18,F150,000 deaths will be prevented in
OL,19,FEngland by 2100.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
