OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778666815
OL,3,CAlmost two-thirds of Brits would back
OL,4,Csmoke and vape-free pub gardens, poll
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FAsh is also calling on the government
OL,8,Fto develop a plan to reduce smoking in
OL,9,Fthe home, particularly around children.
OL,11,FIt also said there should be a vape-
OL,12,Ffree exemption applied in smoking
OL,13,Fcessation services to ensure smokers
OL,14,Fare still encouraged to switch to e-
OL,15,Fcigarettes to quit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
