CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778666815
OL,3,CAlmost two-thirds of Brits would back
OL,4,Csmoke and vape-free pub gardens, poll
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "The Tobacco and
OL,9,FVapes Act is a historic step towards
OL,10,FBritain's first smoke-free generation,
OL,11,Fprotecting them from the harms of
OL,12,Fsmoking and delivering on our ambition
OL,13,Ffor a smoke-free UK.
OL,15,F"Our consultation on free-from places
OL,16,Fclosed on Friday and we are carefully
OL,17,Fconsidering responses.
OL,26,@pD@TOUwD@AOU
