PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778666815
OL,3,CAlmost two-thirds of Brits would back
OL,4,Csmoke and vape-free pub gardens, poll
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"As part of the consultation, we set
OL,8,Fout our proposals to make a number of
OL,9,Fsettings smoke, vape and heated
OL,10,Ftobacco-free ` including kids
OL,11,Fplaygrounds and outside schools.
OL,13,F"We also proposed making indoor spaces
OL,14,Fwhere smoking is already banned vape-
OL,15,Ffree and heated tobacco-free.
OL,17,F"This strikes the right balance right
OL,18,Fbetween protecting the most vulnerable
OL,19,Fand limiting any potential negative
OL,20,Fimpacts on businesses."
